'''詹姆士·海皮'''（{{lang-en|James Heappey}}，{{bd|1981年|1月30日}}）是一位[[英格蘭|英格蘭]]政治人物，他的黨籍是[[保守黨_(英國)|保守黨]]。自2015年開始，他擔任[[韋爾斯_(英國國會選區)|韋爾斯]]選區選出的英國下議院議員<ref>{{cite web|title=Wells|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/politics/constituencies/E14001026|publisher=BBC|accessdate=8 May 2015|archive-date=2015-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150703200517/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/politics/constituencies/E14001026|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他畢業於[[伯明翰大學|伯明翰大學]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Wells|url=http://ukpollingreport.co.uk/2015guide/wells/|publisher=UK Polling Report|accessdate=8 May 2015|archive-date=2016-06-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160613113009/http://ukpollingreport.co.uk/2015guide/wells/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=James Heappey|url=http://www.mhpc.com/election2015/candidates/james-heappey/|publisher=MHP|accessdate=8 May 2015}}{{dead link|date=十月 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Wells MP Conservative hopeful James Heappey meets Compton Bishop and Cross Conservatives|url=http://www.westerndailypress.co.uk/Wells-MP-Conservative-hopeful-James-Heappey-meets/story-18382628-detail/story.html|accessdate=8 May 2015|work=Western Daily Press|date=11 March 2013|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150518071015/http://www.westerndailypress.co.uk/Wells-MP-Conservative-hopeful-James-Heappey-meets/story-18382628-detail/story.html|archivedate=2015年5月18日}}</ref>。

